text:
Stayed at this aparthotel throughout my a week's visit in Paris. This premise has lived up to the Group's standard. My room was clean and spacious, and I was lucky to have a little balcony where I enjoyed my morning coffee and evening drinks, with a Paris Ian skyline.
The location is perfect as:
1. There are a few metro stations (Bregeut-Sabin, Chemin Vert, Bastille) just around the corners, where you can easy take a metro line without changing;
2. Plenty of cafes, bistro and restaurants in the neighbourhood;
3. It's just some 15 mins' walk to Le Marais, a chic shopping area, and within walking proximity to Notre Dame; you may also find lots of boutiques a few streets away in Saint Sebastian Froissart & Republique.
Would definitely stay here again in my next visit to Paris.
